# Ignore from Claude Code auto-context discovery.
# These files should not be pulled into context for general tasks.
# Note: .claudeignore does not PREVENT access — just excludes from auto-discovery.
# For secrets, use permissions.deny in .claude/settings.json instead.

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SPRINT-SPECIFIC CONTEXT MANAGEMENT (post-2nd-audit)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Comment / uncomment these lines based on current sprint.
# Rule: hide what's not needed for current sprint.

# NARRATIVE.md is ONLY needed for Sprint 6 (Archetypes + Endings narrative).
# Keep it hidden for all other sprints.
docs/NARRATIVE.md

# POSTLAUNCH.md is v1.1+ content and should NEVER be loaded during v1.0 dev.
# Do NOT comment this line. Ever. Until v1.0 has shipped.
docs/POSTLAUNCH.md

# UI_MOCKUPS.html is a large visual reference — Claude Code can read it on
# demand (Sprints 2, 11b), but should not auto-load it.
docs/UI_MOCKUPS.html

